      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This used car is in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear with a few small scratches and light scuffs, but no significant dents or paint damage. The interior is well-maintained with moderate wear on high-contact surfaces. The mechanical components are in good working order.",
      "price": 33500.0,
