    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's a great opportunity to get into a dependable, well-maintained vehicle without breaking the bank! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been cared for and runs reliably, with the kind of minor cosmetic wear you'd expect from a vehicle that's been enjoyed on the road. The interior is clean and comfortable, and mechanically it's in solid shape, ready for many more miles of worry-free driving. If you're looking for a trustworthy ride at a fair price, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 36000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper or a parts car with potential? This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant mechanical issues and noticeable cosmetic wear that will require attention before it's road-ready. It's best suited for a handy buyer, a mechanic, or someone looking for a project car they can work on at their own pace. Priced to reflect its current state, this is a great opportunity for the right buyer to get a deal and put in some elbow grease!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make your decision. The exterior shows its age \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some paint fading, and a few small dents that are visible upon close inspection. The interior has seen regular use, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the door panels, and minor staining on the seats. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it has some age-related wear you should be aware of: expect that certain components may need attention in the near term, and we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by your own mechanic. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and steering \u2014 are functional, though not without the quirks you'd expect from a vehicle of this age and use. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for basic reliable transportation at an accessible price point, with the understanding that some investment in upkeep may be needed down the road.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and prospective buyers should have clear, realistic expectations before purchasing. The exterior shows substantial wear, including multiple noticeable dents, deep scratches, and areas of rust or paint fading that go beyond typical cosmetic blemishes. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general signs of hard use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 buyers should budget for repairs and strongly consider a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. This listing is best suited for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle, those seeking parts, or individuals who need basic transportation and are prepared to invest in bringing the car up to a better standard. No major mechanical surprises are being hidden; what you see is genuinely what you get.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable & Honest \u2013 A Budget Buy for the Practical Shopper! \ud83d\ude97\n\nNot every car needs to be perfect to serve a purpose \u2014 and this one is priced to reflect exactly where it stands! This vehicle is in poor condition, meaning it has visible wear, mechanical issues that will need attention, and is best suited for someone comfortable with repairs or looking for a low-cost project. The upside? You're getting into a vehicle at one of the lowest price points on the market, making it a real option for tight budgets or handy buyers. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects that honestly. If you're a DIY enthusiast or just need basic point-A-to-point-B transportation and can handle some TLC, this could be your opportunity! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you about what you're purchasing. The exterior shows significant deterioration \u2014 expect heavy scratching, multiple dents, faded and peeling paint in several areas, and possible rust or corrosion on body panels. The interior is similarly worn, with damaged upholstery, cracked or broken trim pieces, and general neglect throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle or someone looking for parts. It may start and move under its own power, but we would not represent it as reliable daily transportation without substantial repair work. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the true state of the vehicle, and we encourage any serious buyer to conduct a thorough inspection before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
